{
  "stem": "27129.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so they couldn't move fast enough, the military, with horses and cows.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, people were scared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they kept running.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Germans were bombing the-- the main routes, you know, where people were running.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't care.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were-- they lowered the airplanes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were shooting from machine guns and-- and dropping gre-- grenades and bombs, you know, on the cities.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were bombing, you know, with-- with fire bombs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they set a lot of buildings afire.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a horrible, horrible thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When night-- when night came, you know, it was like hell.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, when they start shooting, you know, we ran into the field and we laid down on-- on the ground so maybe they wouldn't hit-- hit me or-- a lot of people didn't get up.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They got killed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then what happened, one of my brothers went far enough-- so because he went with a friend and he lived in a small town on the other side of the Vistula.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a-- oh, what was it?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How they say in English?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like the Volga.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A river, the river Volga.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, so he thought that with him he was going to be safe.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my other brother and myself, we-- we walked until-- because everybody said that-- that we have to go to Warsaw, and over there the Polish army will be able to push back the Germans.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So everybody was run-- was running in this direction.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when we came closer to Warsaw, the Germans caught up with us, you know, and we figured there's no point in going any farther, because the Germans are already ahead of us, and they're going to be in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 40
    }
  ],
